{
  "stem": "10162.4",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was like a self-made man because of who he was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But he came from a very modest background.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was the capitalist background.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I didn't dare to open my mouth anyway, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because I was a class alien.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So everybody was scared in those-- in those days in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were the worst, worst days of Stalinism.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We who went through the days of-- the years of Nazism, we knew that no matter how bad it is, it's not as bad as that was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, it even hardened our differences.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was-- it was horrendous.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was just the fear and the-- the lying, the-- that was the worst part.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was the worst part, that you had to lie to your own child.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you didn't dare to-- you were afraid you would speak in your dream.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because actually the expression that the walls have ears were true.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so we-- we just lived-- another thing for the Jews who went back to their homeland, which was Stalinist Russian satellite countries, Soviet satellite countries, was an added thing, because you went home, and you were not allowed to talk about what you went through.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You were not allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was almost-- it was like they made you ashamed of what you went through.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If you would say something that-- well, in my case, when I went back and I saw what's happening, at one point I wanted to go out-- go back to Germany to the American-- this American camp.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I got as far as Slovakia, and they put me into a camp because I was Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, suddenly I was Hungarian there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then they let me out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I went back to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
